# Plausible Analytics (privacy-focused alternative to Google Analytics)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN="ray.rw"

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# 
# 1. Google OAuth is configured in Supabase Dashboard, NOT in env vars ✅ DONE
# 2. DATABASE_URL uses connection pooling (PgBouncer) for better performance
# 3. DIRECT_URL is only used during prisma migrate commands
# 4. CRON_SECRET must match what you configure in Vercel Cron settings
# 5. All SUPABASE_* keys are case-sensitive
# 6. URLs should NOT have trailing slashes
# 
# SETUP CHECKLIST:
# ☑️ Replace all placeholder values with real credentials ✅ DONE
# ☐ Test locally: npm run build && npm start
# ☑️ Verify Google OAuth works end-to-end ✅ DONE
# ☐ Test database connection: npx prisma db pull
# ☐ Test rate limiting: Try rapid API requests
# ☐ Test cron endpoint: curl -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CRON_SECRET" http://localhost:3000/api/cron/expire-listings
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
